<li><a href="http://www.uni.edu/~gotera/gradapp/stmtpurpose.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.uni.edu/~gotera/gradapp/stmtpurpose.htm" rel="nofollow">How to Write a Great Statement of Purpose</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.sjsu.edu/faculty/gcallaghan/graduate/winningstatement.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sjsu.edu/faculty/gcallaghan/graduate/winningstatement.htm" rel="nofollow">Writing a Statement of Purpose</a></li>
<li><a href="http://career.berkeley.edu/Grad/GradStatement.stm" class="external text" title="http://career.berkeley.edu/Grad/GradStatement.stm" rel="nofollow">Career Center - Graduate School - Statement</a></li>
